===Awards===
* [[Spanish Cross]] in Bronze (6 June 1939)<ref name="Busch and R<U+00F6>ll p258"/>
* [[Memel Medal|The Return of Memel Commemorative Medal]] (26 October 1939)<ref name="Busch and R<U+00F6>ll p258"/>
* [[Iron Cross]] (1939)
** 2nd Class (16 November 1939)<ref name="Busch and R<U+00F6>ll p258"/>
** 1st Class (27 April 1940)<ref name="Busch and R<U+00F6>ll p258"/>
* [[Sudetenland Medal|The Return of Sudetenland Commemorative Medal of 1 October 1938]] (6 November 1940)<ref name="Busch and R<U+00F6>ll p258"/>
* [[Destroyer War Badge]] (24 December 1940)<ref name="Busch and R<U+00F6>ll p258"/>
* [[German Cross]] in Gold on 2 February 1942 as ''[[Kapit<U+00E4>nleutnant]]'' on torpedo boat ''Jaguar''/6. Torbedoboots-Flottille<ref>Patzwall and Scherzer 2001, p. 166.</ref>
* [[U-boat War Badge]] (1939) (17 March 1942)<ref name="Busch and R<U+00F6>ll p258"/>
* [[Knight's Cross of the Iron Cross]] on 17 September 1942 as ''[[Korvettenkapit<U+00E4>n]]'' and commander of ''U-156''<ref>Fellgiebel 2000, p. 214.</ref><ref>Scherzer 2007, p. 367.</ref>
* Mentioned in the [[Wehrmachtbericht]] on 6 June 1942

